last night, so...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Ahh, I get it. That's why you're here to borrow some of our costumes. Okay, you can borrow whatever isn't being used.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"Are you sure it's not a problem...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode197-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"It's no problem at all. The unused costumes really never get used again, so they're just kept in storage.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"They're kind of just going to waste. I'm sure the costumes would be happier with someone wearing them!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Thank you so much, Maya-senpai!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"The costumes are all kept in these closets here, so feel free to take a look.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"The number of closets alone is amazing. How are we going to go about this...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode197-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"True, it's a little overwhelming, isn't it? How about I pick some out for you?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Hmm, let's see. What would suit you two best...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Maya-senpai, do you have any matching outfits? I was thinking it'd be nice if we could wear something like that.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Okay! In that case... try this closet.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Can I look too?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Of course! There's no need to be shy!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Wow~! Tomoe, look at this! There's so many amazing costumes!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"These are impressive... It's going to be hard to choose.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode197-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Our drama club performs all kinds of plays. When they finish, all of the costumes end up here and they just keep piling up.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"It's really hard to keep track of everything, so I wish we could be a bit more on top of it...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"True, our drama club is quite serious and they have a high standard for their costumes, so I can imagine it getting hectic in here.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode197-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Of course! The drama club is home to Kaoru-senpai and Maya-senpai, after all!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"... Ahh~! Check this one out, Tomoe! I wanna wear this~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Umm, this is...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"These fangs... Is this a vampire costume?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode197-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Yeah, I think so! It's so cute, don't you think~? It's totally Halloween!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"That's true, but... don't you think it's a little... revealing?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode197-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"Ahaha, it definitely is one of the more exciting outfits...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"But I really wanna wear this! Please, Tomoe!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"I'm not even sure this will suit me...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"episode197-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Don't worry! You'll look great! I really wanna see what you'll look like in this!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"Maya","body":"True, I'm kind of curious too~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"episode197-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Right? Right~? Even Maya-senpai thinks so! C'mon, Tomoe~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"episode197-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySo